### Step 6: Add More Tests

You can add as many tests as needed by following the same steps, ensuring each test runs in a Docker container and captures screenshots.

### Conclusion

By following these steps, you will have a robust Cypress testing framework that leverages Docker and can capture screenshots of your test results. This setup allows you to run tests in isolated Docker containers, ensuring that your tests are clean and do not interfere with each other.

