- `\foreach \r in {1,2,3,4,5,6,7,8,9}`: Loops through each rank (row) of the chessboard.
- `\foreach \c in {1,2,3,4,5,6,7,8,9}`: Loops through each file (column) of the chessboard.
- `\fill (\r.\c) rectangle ++(1,2) -- (\r.\c+1,2) -- (\r.\c+1,1) -- (\r.\c+1,2)`: Fills the cells with a black color and draws the lines connecting the cells.

